summary: Defines placeholder (dummy) Flax pipeline classes for various Stable Diffusion use‑cases (standard, XL, ControlNet, image‑to‑image, inpainting) that raise informative errors when the required Flax/transformers backends are unavailable.
business_intent: Enable the library to be imported and used without installing heavy Flax or Transformers dependencies, while preserving the public API and providing clear guidance to users about missing backend support.
